file.content:
info: title: BrAPI version: '' openapi: 3.0.0 paths: {} components: schemas: ProgramNewRequest: type: object properties: abbreviation: description: An abbreviation which represents this program type: string example: P1 additionalInfo: additionalProperties: type: string description: Additional arbitrary info type: object commonCropName: description: Common name for the crop which this program is for type: string example: Tomatillo documentationURL: description: A URL to the human readable documentation of this object format: uri type: string example: https://wiki.brapi.org leadPersonDbId: description: The unique identifier of the program leader type: string example: fe6f5c50 leadPersonName: description: The name of the program leader type: string example: Bob Robertson objective: description: The primary objective of the program type: string example: Make a better tomatillo programName: description: Human readable name of the program type: string example: Tomatillo_Breeding_Program programType: description: |- The type of program entity this object represents
'STANARD' represents a standard, permenant breeding program
'PROJECT' represents a short term project, usually with a set time limit based on funding type: string enum: - STANARD - PROJECT example: STANARD fundingInformation: description: Information describing the grant or funding source for this program type: string example: 'EU: FP7-244374' externalReferences: $ref: '#/components/schemas/ExternalReferences'
